trans-unit.source: Provides qualifying information to a callback method when a <see cref="E:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerApplication.ApplicationChanged" /> event occurs.
trans-unit.target: Proporciona información a un método de callback para distinguir cuándo se produce un evento <see cref="E:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerApplication.ApplicationChanged" />.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.ContactManager.ApplicationChanged> event is raised when:
trans-unit.target: Un <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.ContactManager.ApplicationChanged> evento se desencadena cuando:

trans-unit.source: A peer starts an application within a collaboration
trans-unit.target: Un elemento del mismo nivel inicia una aplicación en una colaboración

trans-unit.source: A peer ends an application within a collaboration
trans-unit.target: Un elemento del mismo nivel finaliza una aplicación en una colaboración

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerContact> object that represents a collaborating peer has a change in its properties, such as the associated Nickname
trans-unit.target: La <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerContact> objeto que representa un par de colaboración tiene un cambio en las propiedades, como el alias asociado

trans-unit.source: The scope of the application is changed on that peer contact's computer
trans-unit.target: Se cambia el ámbito de la aplicación en el equipo del contacto del mismo nivel

trans-unit.source: A peer moves to a different IP address on the network
trans-unit.target: Un punto se desplaza a una dirección IP diferente de la red

trans-unit.source: Every class that uses the <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.ApplicationChangedEventArgs> class requires a <xref:System.Security.Permissions.PermissionState> of Unrestricted.
trans-unit.target: Cada clase que se usa el <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.ApplicationChangedEventArgs> clase requiere un <xref:System.Security.Permissions.PermissionState> Unrestricted.

trans-unit.source: This state is created when the <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerCollaboration> object is constructed.
trans-unit.target: Este estado se crea cuando la <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerCollaboration> se haya construido.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerApplication" /> for which the event was raised.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene el <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerApplication" /> para el que se Genera el evento.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerApplication" /> instance that was updated.
trans-unit.target: Instancia de <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerApplication" /> que se actualizó.

trans-unit.source: Unless specified, the default value for this property is `null`.
trans-unit.target: A menos que se especifique, el valor predeterminado de esta propiedad es `null`.

trans-unit.source: Gets the type of change to the <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerApplication" /> that occurred.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene el tipo de cambio que se produjo en el objeto <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerApplication" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerChangeType" /> enumeration value that specifies the type of change that was performed on the <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerApplication" />.
trans-unit.target: Valor de enumeración <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerChangeType" /> que especifica el tipo de cambio que se realizó en <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerApplication" />.

trans-unit.source: Unless specified, the default value for this property is `null`.
trans-unit.target: A menos que se especifique, el valor predeterminado de esta propiedad es `null`.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerContact" /> associated with the <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerApplication" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene el objeto <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerContact" /> asociado a <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerApplication" />.

trans-unit.source: <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerContact" /> associated with the <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerApplication" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerContact" /> asociado a <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerApplication" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the endpoint for which <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerApplication" /> information has changed.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene el extremo cuya información de <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerApplication" /> ha cambiado.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerEndPoint" /> that contains the endpoint for which application information has changed.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerEndPoint" /> que contiene el extremo cuya información de aplicación ha cambiado.

trans-unit.source: Unless explicitly specified, the default value for all properties is <see langword="null" /> for reference types and zero (0) for properties of type <see langword="int" />.
trans-unit.target: A menos que se especifique explícitamente, el valor predeterminado de todas las propiedades es <see langword="null" /> para los tipos de referencia y cero (0) para las propiedades de tipo <see langword="int" />.
